## Appendix A ŌĆö AG-UI events and how V2 uses them

| Event                                    | Consumed?             |
| ---------------------------------------- | --------------------- |
| `RUN_STARTED`                            | No                    |
| `RUN_FINISHED`                           | Yes ŌĆö `metadata.output` |
| `RUN_ERROR`                              | Yes ŌĆö resolves FAILED |
| `TEXT_MESSAGE_START`                     | No (implicit)         |
| `TEXT_MESSAGE_CONTENT`                   | Yes ŌĆö buffer          |
| `TEXT_MESSAGE_END`                       | Yes ŌĆö flush text part |
| `TOOL_CALL_START/ARGS/END/RESULT`        | No                    |
| `STEP_STARTED` / `STEP_FINISHED`         | No                    |
| `STATE_SNAPSHOT` / `STATE_DELTA`         | No                    |
| `REASONING_ENCRYPTED_VALUE`              | No                    |
| `CUSTOM / PV_PRE_RENDER`                 | Yes ŌĆö open PV buffer  |
